Pont will fare financially in the current quarter, adding
that it is company policy not to comment on specific earnings
projections. Noting that in the first quarter the company
nearly matched year-earlier earnings per share, reporting 88
cents a share compared with 90 cents a share in 1990's first
quarter, he added, "we don't see a major short fall" this
year compared with last year.
